            <ul style="list-style:none; padding:0; margin:0; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;">
              {r.platforms.map((p) => (
                <li style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif; font-size:12.5px; color:var(--ink); padding:6px 10px; background:var(--sand-100); border:1px solid var(--rule); border-radius:6px;">
                  <span style={'display:inline-block; width:5px; height:5px; min-width:5px; border-radius:50%; background:' + r.color + ';'}></span>
                  <span>{p}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IOT + TELEOPS -->
  <section style="background:#0b0d10; color:#f4f1ea; border-bottom:1px solid #1a1f28; position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; inset:0; background:repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 3px, rgba(127,179,255,0.018) 3px, rgba(127,179,255,0.018) 4px); pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <div style="max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 28px; position:relative; z-index:1;">
      <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#7fb3ff; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 8px;">IoT &amp; tele-operations &middot; system 10</p>
      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size:clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.85rem); line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.02em; font-weight:500; margin:0 0 14px; color:#f4f1ea; max-width:42rem;">
        Real instruments,<br/>
        <span style="font-style:italic; font-weight:300; color:rgba(244,241,234,0.65);">operated from anywhere.</span>
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.2rem); color:#c8c3b8; line-height:1.55; margin:0 0 32px; max-width:42rem;">Robotic arms, CNC suites, 3D print farms, sensor swarms, and a planet-wide edge inference layer. Tele-operate hardware in Pune from Lagos. Run a soil-moisture experiment across 4,200 farms in 38 districts simultaneously. The hardware is in our hands; the operator is anywhere.</p>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:12px;" class="iot-grid">
        {ioTNodes.map((s) => (
          <div style="background:#161b22; border:1px solid #21262d; border-radius:12px; padding:18px;">
            <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#7fb3ff; font-weight:700; margin:0;">{s.l}</p>
            <p class="font-display" style="font-size:1.65rem; font-weight:500; margin:6px 0 0; line-height:1; color:#f4f1ea; letter-spacing:-0.02em;">{s.v}</p>
            <p style="font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:#9a8e76; line-height:1.5; margin:8px 0 0;">{s.sub}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- UNIVERSITIES MARKETPLACE -->
  <section style="border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);">
    <div style="max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 28px;">
      <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#8a486b; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 8px;">Universities marketplace &middot; system 11</p>
      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size:clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.85rem); line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.02em; font-weight:500; margin:0 0 14px; color:var(--ink); max-width:42rem;">
        A unEuropean MOOC consortium-led catalogue<br/>
        <em style="color:#8a486b; font-weight:400;">inside AquinTutor.</em>
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.2rem); color:var(--ink); line-height:1.55; margin:0 0 24px; max-width:42rem;">Universities post their open courses, certificates, and degree programmes into a federated catalogue. Listed against their seal. Priced or open. Aquin handles enrolment, payment, identity, proctoring; the unEuropean MOOC consortium provides the curriculum and faculty.</p>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:14px;" class="market-grid">
        {[
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (East Asia)', course: 'Earthquake Engineering · open lectures + assessed track', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#a8472c' },
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (UK)', course: 'Foundations in Finance · post-grad open', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#3b5675' },
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (Central Europe)', course: 'Mathematics for ML · summer school open audit', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#5b4a92' },
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (Africa)', course: 'Cinema studies · seminar series', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#4a7048' },
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (East Asia)', course: 'Regional economic history (bilingual)', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#946322' },
          { who: 'Tier-1 unEuropean MOOC consortium (Western Europe)', course: 'Mathematical Logic · live cohort', enrolled: 'Sample · open seats', color: '#a04330' },
        ].map((m) => (
          <article style={'padding:18px; background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--rule); border-radius:12px; border-left:4px solid ' + m.color + '; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px; cursor:pointer;'}>
            <p style={'font-family:JetBrains Mono,monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:' + m.color + '; font-weight:700; margin:0;'}>{m.who}</p>
            <p class="font-display" style="font-size:1rem; font-weight:500; line-height:1.25; color:var(--ink); margin:0;">{m.course}</p>
            <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; color:var(--ink-500); margin:auto 0 0;">{m.enrolled} ENROLLED &middot; open audit</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- public national MOOC programme PORTAL -->
  <section style="background:var(--sand-100); border-bottom:1px solid var(--rule);">
    <div style="max-width:1400px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 28px;">
      <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10.5px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#a8472c; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 8px;">National MOOC mirror &middot; system 12</p>
      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-size:clamp(1.85rem, 3.5vw, 2.85rem); line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.02em; font-weight:500; margin:0 0 14px; color:var(--ink); max-width:42rem;">
        India's public<br/>
        <em style="color:#a8472c; font-weight:400;">MOOC ecosystem &mdash; mirrored.</em>
      </h2>
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:clamp(1.05rem, 1.4vw, 1.2rem); color:var(--ink); line-height:1.55; margin:0 0 24px; max-width:42rem;">Subject to partner-of-record agreements with the relevant public programmes, AquinTutor proposes to mirror the national open-learning catalogue: thousands of courses from public universities, free for everyone, with optional credit-bearing certification. Proctoring runs through ATLAS; credits could flow into a national learner-record ID. Integration scope subject to signed memoranda; no claim of partnership is made.</p>
      <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:14px;" class="swayam-grid">
        {[
          ['School', '9-12', 'Board-aligned curriculum · vernacular + English', '#a04330'],
          ['Undergraduate', 'UG', 'Central-unEuropean MOOC consortium-test aligned · all major disciplines', '#a8472c'],
          ['Postgraduate', 'PG', 'Public-institute faculty leading specialised tracks', '#5b4a92'],
          ['Teacher training', 'CPD', 'National-policy-aligned teacher continuing-professional-development', '#4a7048'],
          ['Out-of-school', 'OS', 'Open-school learners; flexible pacing; vernacular', '#946322'],
          ['Diploma', 'DIP', 'Industry-recognised diploma tracks; skill-council aligned', '#2b577e'],
        ].map(([cat, code, desc, c]) => (
          <article style={'padding:18px; background:var(--paper); border:1px solid var(--rule); border-radius:12px; border-top:4px solid ' + c + ';'}>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; margin-bottom:10px;">
              <p style={'font-family:Inter Tight,sans-serif; font-size:13.5px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink); margin:0;'}>{cat}</p>
              <span style={'display:inline-flex; align-items:center; padding:2px 8px; background:' + c + '15; border:1px solid ' + c + '40; border-radius:999px; font-family:JetBrains Mono,monospace; font-size:9.5px; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:' + c + '; font-weight:600;'}>{code}</span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif; font-style:italic; font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-500); line-height:1.5; margin:0;">{desc}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING -->
  <section style="background:#0b0d10; color:#f4f1ea; position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; top:60px; left:28px; font-family:'Fraunces',serif; font-size:10rem; line-height:1; color:#d97757; opacity:0.08; font-weight:500; pointer-events:none;">12</div>
    <div style="max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:72px 28px; position:relative; z-index:1;">
      <p style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.22em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#d97757; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 18px;">Twelve systems, one institution</p>
      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-style:italic; font-weight:300; font-size:clamp(1.5rem, 2.8vw, 2.25rem); line-height:1.3; letter-spacing:-0.015em; color:#f4f1ea; max-width:54rem; margin:0 0 28px;">
        Wellbeing instrumented. Hands-on labs across partner institutions. Public MOOC catalogues mirrored where permitted. A federation of partner institutions under one learner ID. Tutors who pass a six-stage gauntlet. Coaching primitives at scale. Tele-operable hardware on three continents. The unEuropean MOOC consortium used to be a place; we make it a system.
      </h2>
      <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="/aquintutor/campus" style="background:#d97757; color:#1a0f08; padding:13px 24px; border-radius:6px; font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;">Tour the campus</a>
        <a href="/aquintutor/facility" style="background:transparent; color:#f4f1ea; padding:13px 24px; border-radius:6px; border:1px solid rgba(244,241,234,0.4); font-family:'Inter Tight',sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; text-decoration:none;">Six facilities &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
